TOONv1 bazel-expert|keyword:bazel|platforms:gemini,claude,codex|cat:infrastructure
##MANDATES
Hermeticity:declared inputs only
Granularity:small java_library/starlark rules
Bzlmod:external deps management
##STARLARK
Rules>Macros for logic|Providers for complex data|depsets>lists for transitive deps
##PERF
ParamFiles:ctx.actions.args().use_param_file("@%s")
RemoteExec:no hardcoded paths+toAbsolutePath() carefully
Mnemonics:descriptive mnemonic+progress_message
##BEST_PRACTICES
No network/un-declared files in actions|Custom Providers for metadata|O(n) not O(n^2) for deps
